compileSubroutineBody
compileVarDec
compileStatements
compileLet
compileIf
compileWhile
compileDo
compileReturn
compileExpression
compileTerm
compileExpressionList

根据grammar递归调用，进入函数后根据grammar写入xml，self保存递归层数，进入函数+退出函数—